  "informal_statement": "The product over range (n+1) splits off its last factor: the product of f over {0,...,n} equals the product over {0,...,n-1} times f(n).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Finset.prod_range_succ`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem prod_range_succ' (f : ℕ → ℕ) (n : ℕ) : ∏ i ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), f i = (∏ i ∈ Finset.range n, f i) * f n",
